contract.description: (2020) For an unknown reason baked goods are flying off the shelves and more eggs are needed to restock!

contract.name: Study Diet
contract.description: A seemingly limitless number of tests are being taken: SAT, ACT, AP, LSAT, ETC. The latest prep fad is a Superfood Egg diet. Stores are sold out!

contract.name: Mothers are Forever
contract.description: A "Super Diamond" manufacturer is betting on big spending this mother's day, ordering massive quantities of ingredients.

contract.name: Quantum Solo
contract.description: A Logistics Company has ordered a large batch of Quantum Eggs. For your eyes only.

contract.name: LEGGACY: Supermarket Refill
contract.description: (2020) With so many restaurants closed, supermarkets weren't ready for Edible Egg demand for Mother's day omelettes!

contract.name: Eggclipse
contract.description: Watching the Eclipse from space was so popular this year, multiple space tourism companies need their fuel refilled!

contract.name: Fusion Headphones
contract.description: Sonegg released new wireless headphones powered by fusion eggs that never need to be recharged!

contract.name: Super Hot Dogs
contract.description: A new hot dog engineered from Super Material eggs is a huge hit this Memorial Day - Manufacturers need a restock!

contract.name: Bake Sale
contract.description: The world's largest school district is having the world's largest Bake Sale to solve budget issues. They need supplies!

contract.name: Yolk Screen
contract.description: A new type of sunscreen made from Medical Egg Yolk is rapidly gaining popularity. With summer starting, supplies are needed!

contract.name: Juneteenth
contract.description: Time-travel tours are overrun by young kids learning about the road to freedom for Black Americans. More supplies are needed!

contract.name: Epic Fireworks
contract.description: A few satellite launch services startups are making a few extra bucks making massive sub-orbital fireworks - orders are in!

contract.name: Quantum Seating
contract.description: 4th of July crowds are historic, quantum grandstands allow 10x capacity and have sold out, manufacturers need supplies!

contract.name: Preparations
contract.description: Farmers across the galaxy are decorating their farms, and even their chickens in preparation for Egg Day, raw materials needed!

contract.name: LEGGACY: Tax Headache
contract.description: (2019) It's time to file taxes! Headache cures are in high demand. Help fill the orders!

contract.name: Donuts
contract.description: Donuts are surging in popularity again - both in store and at home. The incredible, edible is in high demand.

contract.name: Sonegg Boom
contract.description: An aerospace startup has begun deployment of its Fusion powered, super-sonic passenger plane, Bock 1. Specialty fuel is needed.

contract.name: School Supplies
contract.description: Shippers are having to contend with an unexpectedly high amount of school supplies to deliver, quantum technology is required!

contract.name: Luncheggbles
contract.description: With school about to resume, pre-made school lunches are ramping production, the top ingredient is Superfood eggs!

contract.name: Infleggtion
contract.description: A new USDE program is incentivizing Super Material Egg production to alleviate supply chain constraints. Time to cash in!

contract.name: Arteggmis I
contract.description: A new rocket system is about to undergo a lengthy testing regime, extensive Rocket Fuel Egg reserves are being ordered.

contract.name: Egg Brain
contract.description: A new Medical Egg Based supplement is being recommended for everyone over 50 to maintain brain heath - much less expensive than Immortality Egg treatments!

contract.name: Depleted Reserves
contract.description: After an extended heat wave, Fusion Egg reserves are nearly depleted, and order are going out!

contract.name: Quantum Fitting
contract.description: Everyone is updating their wardrobe using Quantum fitting rooms: shop online, but instantly try on clothes at home!

contract.name: Challah
contract.description: With the Jewish High Holidays around the corner, edible eggs are flying off the shelves to make delicious Challah bread. Time to restock!

contract.name: Eggutane
contract.description: A new acne treatment made from Medical eggs has been approved. 100% effective with no side effects! Supplies are needed.

contract.name: Launch Boom
contract.description: With insatiable demand for orbital launch services, new providers are reaching for the stars - fuel is needed!

contract.name: Pumpkin Art
contract.description: Pumpkin decorating contests are the activity of choice for kids this year, stores are paying a premium for pumpkins!

contract.name: Class Projeggts
contract.description: The first big school projects are coming due, from Model Spiders, to Dioramas craft stores around the country need more supplies!

contract.name: Chapocalypse
contract.description: With chocolate supply chains disrupted, There's a huge shortage of Halloween treats this year. Act fast!

contract.name: Quantum Candy
contract.description: Quantum trash bags are sold out as candy enthusiasts retrofit halloween baskets with them for unlimited candy collection! Help restock!

contract.name: Tooth Saver
contract.description: A new cavity fighting toothpaste is a huge hit as shoppers try to recover from halloween candy indulgence. Active Ingredient: Medical Eggs

contract.name: Storage Storage
contract.description: With a large decrease in container shipping, ports are building massive quantum warehouses to store the empty storage containers - orders are in!

contract.name: Pumpkin Cheesecake
contract.description: Pumpkin Cheesecake is the trendy desert this Thanksgiving, once again surprising suppliers who need more Pumpkin Eggs!

contract.name: Black Fried Egg
contract.description: In store and online deals led to record holiday sales - factories are adding shifts to restock goods - supplies are needed!

contract.name: Snow Energy
contract.description: With farms everywhere covered in snow, Fusion egg powered snow removal tools are spiking demand for their fuel!

contract.name: Water Cup
contract.description: As the World Cup comes to a close, Quatar's desalination plants are tapped, they have ordered more water!

contract.name: Fusion Beakthrough
contract.description: Scientists are attempting to create fusion energy that doesn't require Eggs, but their experiments need so much energy! Orders are in!

contract.name: Knitting Chickens
contract.description: The popularity of knitting has exploded, and the winter weather keeping people indoors has super-material yarn flying off the shelves!

contract.name: Eggflation Reduction
contract.description: The Edible Egg farm system is taking longer to recover from Avian flu than expected and more Egg Farmers are needed!

contract.name: ChatEPT
contract.description: The surge in AI generated content is leading datacenter energy requirements to explode - help supply clean energy!

contract.name: Private Fuel
contract.description: A launch services provider is buying direct and wondering if you're interested?

contract.name: Race Fuel
contract.description: The Daytona 24 hour race is using a new fuel formula derived from Rocket Fuel. They need top grade eggs!

contract.name: Kids First [Aid]
contract.description: Drug stores continue to be sold out of medication for children (why isn't this national news?) Let's raise awareness and help restock!

contract.name: Quantum Vacation
contract.description: The cold weather has led to a surge in vacations to sunnier places - top way to travel? Teleportation.

contract.name: The Classic
contract.description: After a few years out of fashion, Chocolate has returned as this years desired Valentines gift - Chocolate eggs are a top choice.

contract.name: Aerodynameggs
contract.description: The Formula 1 racing season is about to start and teams are iterating rapidly on aerodynamic designs - supplies are ordered!

contract.name: Hall Haul
contract.description: A new micro-satellite constellation is equipped with with Fusion Egg powered Hall thrusters - they've put in an order!

contract.name: Disasters
contract.description: A cluster of Disasters around the world has put Medical Egg supplies at risk - Large Contracts are available to restock.

contract.name: Quantum Banking
contract.description: A new financial technology allows banks to instantly share their reserves to guard against Bank Runs - Quantum eggs are needed!

contract.name: Omegga 3
contract.description: As Omega 3 rich diets gain popularity, Superfood eggs are seen as a top breakfast, orders are surging
